page.title: 19CHILD'S DAY IN BENINGTON (4)
page.content: This was followed by the Adults talking and we children watching T.V. After about 15 mins. we became bored and my sister suggested playing "I Spy". Dad joined in and we played for about 30 mins. I cheated, for a joke, and we stopped playing. 21.30 hr.Had a drink of coke and then set off back home. 22.00 hr.Arrived home and I went to my bedroom, put on my pyjamas and got into bed. I read for about 10 mins. Mum came into my room to say "Goodnight"and told me to stop reading and get to sleep. 22.30 hr.Went to sleep.
